Products.RichDescription:
Lawson's Stone Mill Wholemeal is baked in the spirit and traditions of country Australia, where bread was handmade, took time, was generous in size and full of abundant goodness.

Lawson's Traditional Bread is baked in the spirit and traditions of country Australia, where bread was handmade, took time, was generous in size and full of abundant goodness. In this spirit, these breads are brimming with nature's simplest ingredients and baked in a generous wide tin to deliver a hearty loaf with the best possible flavour and taste.

Back in the pioneer days, flour mills created wholemeal flour rich in flavour and uncompromised in its nutritional value. The Miller, being skilled at his craft, could tell by touch exactly which meal (flour) would produce the best bread. Passed down through generations these skills are utilised to produce this traditional style bread, rich in flavour and colour. This is a healthy, delicious and great tasting loaf. Try it served toasted with a good size chunk of butter.

One serve (2 slices) of Lawson's Stonemill Wholemeal contributes 100% towards the Grains Legumes Nutrition Council 48g Whole Grain Daly Target Intake.

This product contains no artificial preservatives or colours, no animal fats. It is a source of protein and an excellent source of fibre.

Products.Name: Mother Stone Sourdough Sliced
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Mother Stone Sourdough Sliced' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription: Early humans used stones to grind up wild seeds and then added water to make primitive dough for bread. Then, the ancients discovered that leaving the mixture open to the air overnight caused something miraculous to happen: the dough would rise, and gain flavour and texture. Adding a piece (known as the 'mother') to the next batch produced the same effect. Today, we make Mother Stone sourdough in this time-honoured way. Nothing is artificial, and nothing is rushed. We use simple, good ingredients, and then allow the dough to rise slowly and naturally without using commercial yeast. The way it always did before there were additives and industrial processing. It takes us approximately 72 hours to make each loaf, but it's worth it. Mother Stone is rich with flavour, a feast for all the senses. It is as good for you now as it was back then.

AdditionalAttributes.description:
Golden Pancakes contain no artificial colour or flavours.
Scrumptious, fluffy and easy to serve. Never a boring bite!

Golden Pancakes are delicious for breakfast, dessert, or a snack any time. Just heat them up and add your favourite topping. You could pile on juicy berries with a dollop of ice cream, drizzle with maple syrup, or create your own melt-in-your-mouth combo.

Look out for these other delicious Golden products: Golden Crumpets, Golden Crumpet Squares, Gloden Pikelets and Golden Pikelet Bites - Perfect for kids lunchboxes!
